  "rationale": "Ordered as hero \u2192 logos \u2192 features \u2192 testimonial \u2192 cta, mapping the brief onto Remote's captured SaaS patterns. The hero reuses hero-inset-noise-panel (display headline, subhead, filled + outlined CTA pills over the brand's pastel art surface) with the single sanctioned display-title-over-media treatment. Trust comes early via partner-proof-row bound to the 10,000+ stat and four real colored partner logos. The three value_props render as ONE feature-item run in a clean on-grid 3-up cards row adapted from infra-proof-split (archetype swapped to cards to hold the three modules while keeping the proof intent). testimonial-card-row carries the real quote plus two brand-voice-consistent proofs. The cta reuses cta-inline-banner as a centered conversion beat; per the offGridExpansion=false lock the panel-on-media treatment was removed and the banner ships as a disciplined on-grid centered stack on a panel band. No inverse/dark bands, one accent budget honored through actions, sentence-case headings, non-zero radius throughout, footer omitted for the appended brand chrome."
